    "Overlapping scores are adjusted by 0.2 for visual clarity.1) Comparable Usability to Baseline: Overall, the results show that the HINTs is a highly usable and user-friendly system, as we find no significant difference between the selfreported Mental Demand, Effort, and Frustration.",
